General.Name: Regal Funds Management Pty Limited
General.Description: Regal Partners Limited is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm invests in the public equity and hedging markets across the globe with a focus on Australia. It employs market neutral and absolute return strategies to make its investments. The firm also employs fundamental analysis along with bottom up stock picking approach to create its portfolios. Regal Partners Limited was founded in 2004 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
